## Properties

| Property       | Attribute       | Description                                                                       | Type      | Default |
| -------------- | --------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | --------- | ------- |
| `dense`        | `dense`         | Makes the button text and container slightly smaller.                             | `boolean` | `false` |
| `disabled`     | `disabled`      | Disabled buttons cannot be interacted with and have no visual interaction effect. | `boolean` | `false` |
| `icon`         | `icon`          | Indicates the element containing the button's icon.                               | `boolean` | `false` |
| `label`        | `label`         | Indicates the element containing the button's text label.                         | `boolean` | `false` |
| `outlined`     | `outlined`      | Styles an outlined button that is flush with the surface.                         | `boolean` | `false` |
| `raised`       | `raised`        | Styles a contained button that is elevated above the surface.                     | `boolean` | `false` |
| `trailingIcon` | `trailing-icon` | Indicates the element containing the button's trailing icon.                      | `boolean` | `false` |
| `unelevated`   | `unelevated`    | Styles a contained button that is flush with the surface.                         | `boolean` | `false` |
